Author: STUDHOLME
Vol / Page: 108
Edition: 1954
Quote: ... we got a few of the [Steiger sheep] breed ..., but they were not a success, being ... `buffalo headed' and very wool blind.
Notes:

Date: 0/0/1955
Source: Wool Away!
Author: BOWEN
Vol / Page: 64
Edition:
Quote: ... many or our sheep have become wool-blind, ie wool grows over their eyes so that they cannot see.
